Data Fields

pjmedia_tone_desc Struct Reference
[Multi-frequency tone generator]

Data Fields

short freq1
short freq2
short on_msec
short off_msec
short volume
short flags

Detailed Description

This structure describes individual MF digits to be played with pjmedia_tonegen_play().

Field Documentation

short pjmedia_tone_desc::freq1

First frequency.

short pjmedia_tone_desc::freq2

Optional second frequency.

short pjmedia_tone_desc::on_msec

Playback ON duration, in miliseconds.

short pjmedia_tone_desc::off_msec

Playback OFF duration, ini miliseconds.

short pjmedia_tone_desc::volume

Volume (1-32767), or 0 for default, which PJMEDIA_TONEGEN_VOLUME will be used.

short pjmedia_tone_desc::flags

Currently internal flags, must be 0
